Any help?

SysId changed substantially this year (project generation was removed), and the new docs haven’t been completed/merged yet. Draft of the new docs is here: Update SysId docs for 2024 by DeltaDizzy · Pull Request #2492 · wpilibsuite/frc-docs · GitHub

The basic concept is you now instantiate SysIdRoutine in your normal robot program and run it as a command. This captures the data into a log file that then you load into SysId.
